The paper discusses the recent developments in automated machine learning (AutoML), which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of AutoML in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are popular applications of machine learning. Additionally, the paper discusses the need for domain experts to build machine learning applications, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE).
